      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium that perfectly balances rugged capability with everyday comfort. The Super White exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror cap\u2014typical for a vehicle that has been enjoyed but respected. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing only minimal surface oxidation. Inside, the black SofTex interior is in excellent shape; the bolsters on the power-adjustable heated front seats remain firm, and the cabin is free of any odors or pet hair. All electronics, including the Entune Premium Audio with Navigation and the signature power rear window, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this 4Runner is sound, featuring a documented service history with a recent synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. It sits on a set of Michelin Defender tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This SUV tracks straight on the highway and the 4WD system engages smoothly, making it a reliable choice for your next family trip or off-road excursion.",
